Please copy and paste the template below into a new folder for each new blog post.
Remove brackets once you fill in the content.
See "hello_blog" under "blog_templates folder for example post.

---
author: [Fill in author name here]

categories:
- [list 1+ categories that the post may fall under; "MiR Highlights", "Events", etc.]

date: ["YYYY-MM-DD" for blog post date]

draft: [choose true or false -- true if you don't want to post it to the website yet, false if posting to the website immediately]

excerpt: [subtitle/short description goes here]

layout: [single]

title: [Title of the blog post]

subtitle:

tags:
- [list 1+ tags that match the post; "Visualization" "TidyTuesday", etc.]

---
